data.description: Lovely cottage style home listed in SW Caldwell. Centrally located with close proximity to Indian Creek Plaza, College of Idaho, shopping, entertainment, & restaurants. This single level home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, & a bonus/office area at 1479 sqft. Situated on .14 of an acre which includes a 8X16 storage shed with extra alley parking. Mud room, covered patio and spacious kitchen. Within short walking distance to Fairview golf course, Caldwell library, and Sebree park. Irrigation, fully fenced, garden space & alley access. Brand new roof, newer furnace, newer water heater, quartz countertops, and LVP Flooring throughout.
